CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 18, 1967, pg. 13 reads: "Special Recognition - When Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority celebrated its annual Founders Day recently, special recognition was given to members of Alpha Alpha Omega Chapter. Some of them are pictured...the basileus of the AKA graduate chapter.  Left to right Sorors Esther Summers, Kathleen Douglas, Jessie M. Vann, Lee Bertha Nicklos, basileus; Marjorie Harris and..."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority members seated behind rectangular tables. from left: Esther Summers, Kathleen Douglass, Jessie Vann, Lee Bertha Nicklos, Marjorie Harris, and Eleanor Jones, in Stouffers Restaurant during Founders Day celebration
